name: Dissipating of a Belief
description:
What happens if you believe in something and someday your belief turns out to be a big lie? How would you react? 
Angry? Sad? or mostly shocked!
On some level, it may ruin the meaning of your life!

It has its prevention, of course. For the people who don't resist seeing reality!
And it is: Knowing that every belief will dissipate someday.
